name: :Analytics/Geo
description: Indexing, search aggregations of geo points and shapes

name: :Analytics/Rollup
description: Turn fine-grained time-based data into coarser-grained data

name: :Core/Features/Features
description: A catch-all label for :Core/Features that don't fit in any other bucket.

name: :Core/Features/Indices APIs
description: APIs to create and manage indices

name: :Core/Features/Ingest
description: Execution or management of Ingest Pipelines

name: :Core/Features/Java Low Level REST Client
description: Minimal dependencies Java Client for Elasticsearch

name: :Core/Infra/Circuit Breakers
description: Track estimates of memory consumption to prevent overload

name: :Core/Infra/Packaging
description: RPM and deb packaging, tar and zip archives, shell and batch scripts

name: :Core/Infra/Resiliency
description: Keep running when everything is ok. Die quickly if things go horribly wrong.

name: :Distributed/Allocation
description: All issues relating to the decision making around placing a shard (both master logic & on the nodes)

name: :Distributed/CCR
description: Issues around the Cross Cluster State Replication features

name: :Distributed/CRUD
description: A catch all label for issues around indexing, updating and getting a doc by id. Not search.

name: :Distributed/Cluster Coordination
description: Cluster formation and cluster state publication, including cluster membership and fault detection.

name: :Distributed/Discovery-Plugins
description: Anything related to our integration plugins with EC2, GCP and Azure

name: :Distributed/Distributed
description: A catch all label for anything in the Distributed Area. If you aren't sure, use this one.

name: :Distributed/Engine
description: Anything around managing Lucene and the Translog in an open shard.

name: :Distributed/Recovery
description: Anything around constructing a new shard, either from a local or a remote source.

name: :Distributed/Reindex
description: Issues relating to reindex that are not caused by issues further down

name: :Distributed/Snapshot/Restore
description: Anything directly related to the `_snapshot/*` APIs

name: :Distributed/Store
description: Issues around managing unopened Lucene indices. If it touches Store.java, this is a likely label.

name: :Distributed/Task Management
description: Issues for anything around the Tasks API - both persistent and node level.

name: :Performance
description: All issues related to Elasticsearch performance including regressions and investigations

name: :Search/Analysis
description: How text is split into tokens

name: :Search/Highlighting
description: How a query matched a document

name: :Search/Percolator
description: Reverse search: find queries that match a document

name: :Search/Search
description: Search-related issues that do not fall into other categories

name: :Search/Suggesters
description: "Did you mean" and suggestions as you type

name: >test
description: Issues or PRs that are addressing/adding tests

name: >test-mute
description: Use for PR that only mute tests

name: Team:ML
description: Meta label for the ML team

name: Team:QL
description: Meta label for query languages team
